        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A short energy statement for the moment you recognise a parent's money pattern in your own behaviour. Say it as soon as you notice the recognition turning to fear.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to energy statements? Read ",
